zathura-tts (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of Zathura TTS plugin
  * Multiple TTS engine support (Piper-TTS, Speech Dispatcher, espeak-ng)
  * Advanced text extraction and processing capabilities
  * Comprehensive keyboard shortcuts for TTS control
  * Visual feedback with text highlighting during reading
  * Configurable speech settings (speed, volume, voice selection)
  * Special content handling for mathematical formulas and tables
  * Session persistence and reading position memory
  * Extensive documentation and troubleshooting guides
  * Complete test suite with unit and integration tests
  * Developer documentation and API reference

 -- Zathura TTS Development Team <dev@zathura-tts.org>  Sat, 02 Aug 2025 12:00:00 +0000